::Hot Rod::

"I'm just Hot Rod, just another Maximal warrior. But if you go by the
history tapes, I'm Rodimus Prime, sucessor of Optimus Prime, destroyer
of Unicron, savior of Cybertron, ex- Autobot commander, and the Matrix's
chosen one. But I hate all the glory. I really didn't like command." He
pulled a thin metal square, from his chest. The part that showed had the
Maximal symbol, but he showed her the other side, with the Autobot
symbol.
